cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CR, cs.CV, cs.NE

The paper discusses the design and evaluation of a dataset generator for improving the performance of an anomaly detection model. This falls under the broad category of machine learning (cs.LG) and specifically, artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions the use of LSTM-AD, a deep learning model, which is commonly used in computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.NE). Additionally, the paper discusses the importance of correctly identifying anomalies, which is relevant to the field of cybersecurity (cs.CR).
